channel.title: Can't open autospawn.cfg
channel.description:

"Invalid or corrupt jarfile C:\Documents and Settings\Aaron\Desktop\Sources\Fighting Irish Scape\autospawn.cfg"
I've tried this with a few different sources and it still doesn't work, if i need to download anything can you just leave a link.
Thanks, Alot P.S. Been stuck for like a week and anything will help
